Ah, so I just had a bum input for my lambda function. The empty lambda template gives a signature of :
`public string Function(string input, ILambdaContext context)` and I kept getting serialization issues.
After changing it to:
`public string Function(Stream input, ILambdaContext context)` for a string input
Or
```c#
public class Foobar {
   public string foo { get; set; }
}
public string Function(Foobar input, ILambdaContext context)
```
For a serialized JSON input, this worked beautifully
